<li>Sufficient resources and personnel to construct and maintain an Alpha/Thaumiel-class facility, capable of containing all anomalous items granted for use in Project Phantasos.</li>
<li>Access to all documents regarding: Project Maxwell; Project Laplace; <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/olympia-project">Project Olympia</a>; Casefile GM9W-01GM.</li>
